snippet.title: FREEDOM: Diegesis game teaser trailer
snippet.description:
http://freedom.quicksandgames.com

FREEDOM: Diegesis is a free 2D side-scroller game for Windows with puzzle, adventure, and horror elements.


Game mirror at http://gamejolt.com/games/freedom-diegesis/135029


Trailer Shot and Edited by Brad Ardley:

http://www.bradardleyportfolio.com/

Music Credits:
1. "Overwicked" from the FREEDOM: Diegesis soundtrack.

2. "Hep Cats" by Kevin MacLeod (http://www.incompetech.com).
"Hep Cats is" licensed under Creative Commons: By Attribution 3.0
http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/

Thanks to the actors and art team!
